data.description: Exceptional fully renovated 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom tri-level home spanning 2172 sq ft, situated on a one third acre landscaped lot in the prestigious Calico Ridge community. Offering stunning city views including the Las Vegas Strip. This deluxe residence boasts a thoughtfully designed layout, creating a perfect blend of style and functionality. Indulge in luxurious living with spacious bedrooms, with a large balcony off the master bedroom to view the spectacular sunsets over the Las Vegas Strip and mountains. Take a dip in the bubbling spa as you watch the sun rise or set. This home is truly a distinguished choice for those seeking an elevated and sophisticated lifestyle. Your dream home awaits with this special blend of luxury and mesmerizing cityscape.
